      <title>意大利铁路运营商 Ferrovie 将从 Intesa 获得 20 亿欧元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/italy-rail-operator-ferrovie-to-get-2-billion-loan-from-intesa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利国家铁路公司 (Ferrovie dello Stato Italiane SpA) 将从 Intesa Sanpaolo SpA 获得一笔 20 亿欧元（21 亿美元）的贷款，这将帮助这家国有铁路运营商筹集维护资金并加强其基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/italy-rail-operator-ferrovie-to-get-2-billion-loan-from-intesa</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 14:58:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
