      <title>欧洲央行将开始发布关键工资指标，为利率决策提供参考</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/ecb-to-start-publishing-key-wage-gauge-informing-rate-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将定期公布其最有价值的欧元区工资增长追踪指标之一，为影响货币政策决策的分析提供深刻见解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/ecb-to-start-publishing-key-wage-gauge-informing-rate-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 14:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国电网投资计划将推高消费者电费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/uk-grid-investment-plans-set-to-drive-up-bills-for-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国公用事业公司预计将在五年内投资超过 770 亿英镑（980 亿美元）用于升级电网，这将增加消费者的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/uk-grid-investment-plans-set-to-drive-up-bills-for-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 14:12:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国政府要求裕信银行退出德国商业银行股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/germany-says-it-expects-unicredit-to-sell-commerzbank-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在意大利联合信贷银行宣布增持德国商业银行股份数小时后，德国又要求联合信贷银行出售其持有的德国商业银行股份，这进一步加剧了这家德国银行两大股东之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/germany-says-it-expects-unicredit-to-sell-commerzbank-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 13:41:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
